sauna (0.0.5-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Allow users to load extra plugins from their filesystem
  * New plugin Memcached
  * Plugin Processes: new check to monitor file descriptors
  * Plugin Disk: new check to monitor inodes

 -- Nicolas Le Manchet <nicolas@lemanchet.fr>  Fri, 29 Apr 2016 16:03:49 +0200

sauna (0.0.4-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Allow to run multiple consumers in parallel
  * Plugins and consumers are auto-discovered using decorators
  * Improve NSCA consumer reliability in a HA setup
  * New consumer TCP server
  * New plugin Puppet agent
  * New plugin Postfix

 -- Nicolas Le Manchet <nicolas@lemanchet.fr>  Tue, 19 Apr 2016 17:00:33 +0200

